samples.commui
Class Cell

java.lang.Object
  samples.commui.Cell

public class Cell
extends java.lang.Object

This class represents the smallest defined element in a maze. Cells are square, and they represent either a piece of a path, or a piece of a wall. Each cell has eight neighbors, two horizontal, two vertical, and four diagonal. Neigbors for edge or corner cells may be null.
